  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个消息推送的状态流转图。消息最开始是待处理状态，然后可能进入调度或者变成无法处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PENDING",
        "SCHEDULED",
        "UNPROCESSABLE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点是初始节点，然后到PENDING。那SCHEDULED和UNPROCESSABLE都是从PENDING直接过去的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "PENDING",
        "SCHEDULED",
        "UNPROCESSABLE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，PENDING可以直接到SCHEDULED，也可能因为格式问题直接判为UNPROCESSABLE。另外SCHEDULED之后还有个发送请求的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PENDING",
        "SCHEDULED",
        "UNPROCESSABLE",
        "SEND_REQUESTED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把PENDING到SCHEDULED、UNPROCESSABLE的两条线画上，再加上SCHEDULED到SEND_REQUESTED。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PENDING",
        "SCHEDULED",
        "UNPROCESSABLE",
        "SEND_REQUESTED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "SEND_REQUESTED之后有两种结果：发送成功到SENT，或者失败到FAIL_TO_SEND。这两个都是终态。另外SCHEDULED状态还可能被用户删除。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SEND_REQUESTED",
        "SENT",
        "FAIL_TO_SEND",
        "DELETED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "删除也是从SCHEDULED出发吗？那SCHEDULED到UNPROCESSABLE这条线也需要吗，还是只从PENDING过去？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHEDULED",
        "DELETED",
        "UNPROCESSABLE",
        "PENDING"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "SCHEDULED也可以到UNPROCESSABLE，比如调度后发现资源不足。删除和无法处理都连到终止节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHEDULED",
        "DELETED",
        "UNPROCESSABLE",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。SENT、UNPROCESSABLE、FAIL_TO_SEND、DELETED都指向终止节点。我检查一遍：所有终态都有出口到[*]，状态流转都覆盖了。",
